Note: Alfa‚Äôs `Can't Tell` outcomes require manual review ‚Äî they are *not* skipped. This improves audit traceability and supports compliance reporting.

After running the audit, filter by `outcome === 'Can\'t Tell'` and pass those to your review queue:

```ts
