**Architectural distinction:**

| Dimension              | axe-core (`@axe-core/playwright`)          | @siteimprove/alfa-playwright                 |
|------------------------|-------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------|
| **Engine foundation**  | Heuristic + rule-based engine              | Formal logic (W3C ACT rules) + semantic model |
| **Output type**        | JSON object with `violations`, `incomplete`, `passes`, `inapplicable` | `Iterable<RuleResult>` with `outcome` ‚àà {Passed, Failed, Inapplicable, Can't Tell} |
| **Can‚Äôt tell handling**| Not explicitly modeled ‚Äî rolled into `incomplete` | First-class outcome: **requires manual review** |
| **Rule IDs**           | Custom (e.g., `color-contrast`)           | W3C SC aligned (e.g., `'1.4.3'`)             |
